HUMAN RIGHTS COUNCIL 
Thirteenth session 
Agenda item 3 
</p>
<p><b>PROMOTION AND PROTECTION OF ALL HUMAN RIGHTS,  
CIVIL, POLITICAL, ECONOMIC, SOCIAL AND CULTURAL RIGHTS, 
INCLUDING THE RIGHT TO DEVELOPMENT 
</b></p>
<p><b>JOINT STUDY ON GLOBAL PRACTICES IN RELATION TO SECRET  
DETENTION IN THE CONTEXT OF COUNTERING TERRORISM  
OF THE SPECIAL RAPPORTEUR ON THE PROMOTION AND  
PROTECTION OF HUMAN RIGHTS AND FUNDAMENTAL  
FREEDOMS WHILE COUNTERING TERRORISM, MARTIN SCHEININ; 
THE SPECIAL RAPPORTEUR ON TORTURE AND OTHER CRUEL, 
INHUMAN OR DEGRADING TREATMENT OR PUNISHMENT,  
MANFRED NOWAK; THE WORKING GROUP ON ARBITRARY 
