Waleed bin Attash in Karachi, Pakistan, on 29 April 2003 
</p>
<p>&#8226; Mohammed Farik bin Amin (Malaysian), also known as Zubair, captured in Bangkok 
on 8 June 2003 
</p>
<p>&#8226; Riduan Isamuddin (Indonesian), also known as Hambali, also known as Encep 
Nuraman, captured in Ayutthaya, Thailand, on 11 August 2003 
</p>
<p>                                                 
