&#8220;foreign site&#8221;. From the OIG report it seems that Abu Zubaydah and Abd al-Rahim al-Nashiri 
were detained and interrogated at the same place.<b>187</b> This information could not be verified, as 
the location of the interrogation is redacted in the report of the CIA Officer General, although 
