them under exclusive American control and had permitted American &#8220;special purpose planes&#8221; to 
land on the territory of Poland.<b>198 </b>The existence of the facility has always been denied by the 
Government of Poland and press reports have indicated that it is unclear what Polish authorities 
knew about the facility. 
